<div class="artwork-content">
    <div id="artwork-details">
        <div id="tombstone">
   
    <p><strong>05. "Fresher, More Delicious Meals Begin at Sub-Zero." Sub-Zero Freezer Company, Inc.; Madison, WI; 2006.</strong><br />       <p>According to historians, no other room in the modern home has been more &ldquo;radically altered by the technological, social, and aesthetic revolutions of the twentieth century&rdquo; than the kitchen.<a href="3532#_ftn1" name="_ftnref1" title="" id="_ftnref1"> </a> As what had been, historically, a purely functional space transformed into a &ldquo;space central to daily life and social encounters between family and friends,&rdquo;<a href="3532#_ftn2" name="_ftnref2" title="" id="_ftnref2"> </a> consumers sought more than just a place to prepare meals.</p>
<p>The post-war age of affluence was largely the result of a rapid increase in automation, which &ldquo;loosened a fresh windfall of inexpensive goodsâ€¦ to bring more comfort and enjoyment into daily life.&rdquo;<a href="3532#_ftn3" name="_ftnref3" title="" id="_ftnref3"> </a> As the new center of home life, the kitchen benefited from this windfall perhaps more than any other domestic space. </p>
<div>
  <div id="ftn1"><br />
    <a href="3532#_ftnref1" name="_ftn1" title="" id="_ftn1"> </a> Juliet Kinchin with Aidan O&rsquo;Connor, <em>Counter Space: Design and the Modern Kitchen</em>. (New York : Museum of Modern Art, [2011]), 5. </div>
  <div id="ftn2">
    <p><a href="3532#_ftnref2" name="_ftn2" title="" id="_ftn2"> </a> Ibid.</p>
  </div>
  <div id="ftn3">
    <p><a href="3532#_ftnref3" name="_ftn3" title="" id="_ftn3"> </a> &ldquo;Cause of Breakthrough Toward Life of Plenty,&rdquo; <em>Life</em>, 12/28/1959, 36.</p>
  </div>
</div><br /><br />
    	 "Tools of the Trade: 19th- and 20th-Century Architectural Trade Catalogs," Case 5, Ryerson &amp; Burnham Libraries, August 4, 2015-October 12, 2015.<br />
<br />
<a href="https://digital-libraries.artic.edu/cdm/ref/collection/mqc/id/68781">Link to R&amp;B Archives Digital Collections record</a><br />    	    </p>

    </div><!--/tombstone-->
    </div><!--/artwork-details-->
